  "summary": "det(K) distribution across 2977 knots: mean=118.9, median=109.0, skew=0.49. Overall log(det) ~ 0.394*n (R\u00b2=0.127), weak. Alternating only: log(det) ~ 0.543*n (R\u00b2=0.588), strong => det ~ 1.722^n. Within each crossing number class, the distribution is NEITHER cleanly log-normal nor power-law. Mod-prime residues tested for bias."
